WEBVTT

00:00.880 --> 00:01.720
Brother Biaozhi

00:02.040 --> 00:03.280
Long time no see

00:04.080 --> 00:05.880
In the past when I was imprisoned

00:06.040 --> 00:07.880
You saved my life

00:08.000 --> 00:08.800
This friendship

00:09.000 --> 00:10.360
I have always remembered

00:11.320 --> 00:11.920
Open the gates

00:11.920 --> 00:12.880
Surrender to me

00:12.920 --> 00:13.600
In the future

00:14.200 --> 00:15.840
I will not treat you poorly

00:16.040 --> 00:17.000
Enough talk

00:17.600 --> 00:20.000
In the past I saved the one who cared for the world

00:20.200 --> 00:21.720
Aimed at the north, Prince of Jin

00:22.200 --> 00:24.080
Even if I could go back

00:24.080 --> 00:25.480
Even if it meant ending my career

00:25.480 --> 00:27.240
I would still do the same
